%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b957bb3dd05460a4db7af93ce53c5bfb, type: 3}
  m_Name: Bank_Info
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueGraph
  nodes:
  - id: start
    npcText: What exactly explain?
    options:
    - playerText: What is ID and where do I get it?
      nextNodeId: id_howto
      debugEvent: 
    - playerText: How do ATM machines work?
      nextNodeId: atm_howto
      debugEvent: 
    - playerText: Are there any commissions on transactions?
      nextNodeId: fees
      debugEvent: 
    - playerText: How do I know that the system is secure and no one will rob me?
      nextNodeId: security
      debugEvent: 
    - playerText: How to open a bank account and get a credit card?
      nextNodeId: account_howto
      debugEvent: 
    - playerText: Back
      nextNodeId: graph:Start/start
      debugEvent: 
    endAfterNpcLine: 0
  - id: id_howto
    npcText: Every city resident must have a Citizen ID card, which can be obtained
      at the city hall. The ID card is used to create an account at our bank, and
      without it, access or viewing the account is impossible.
    options:
    - playerText: Back
      nextNodeId: start
      debugEvent: 
    endAfterNpcLine: 0
  - id: atm_howto
    npcText: At the ATM, you can perform basic operations such as withdrawing or
      depositing cash into your account, and blocking your card in case of theft.
      After three incorrect PIN attempts, your card may be blocked, requiring a visit
      to one of our staff members.
    options:
    - playerText: Back
      nextNodeId: start
      debugEvent: 
    endAfterNpcLine: 0
  - id: fees
    npcText: Some of our bank's services incur transaction fees, depending on applicable
      city taxes. These include loans, transfers, and ATM withdrawals and withdrawals.
    options:
    - playerText: Back
      nextNodeId: start
      debugEvent: 
    endAfterNpcLine: 0
  - id: security
    npcText: Don't share your credit card PIN with anyone. Report a lost card to
      your bank as soon as possible.
    options:
    - playerText: Back
      nextNodeId: start
      debugEvent: 
    endAfterNpcLine: 0
  - id: account_howto
    npcText: To open a bank account, you'll need a city-issued Resident ID card and
      a $10 fee. The card fee is $5, but it's optional. Transactions can be made
      on-site or at an ATM.
    options:
    - playerText: Back
      nextNodeId: start
      debugEvent: 
    endAfterNpcLine: 0
  startNodeId: start
